[
    {
        "text": "\"Hello, this is Bong\nJoon Ho,",
        "start": 0.5,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "director of 'Parasite.'",
        "start": 2.45,
        "duration": 2.45
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the story\nabout infiltration.",
        "start": 6.3,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "One family infiltrates\nto other family.",
        "start": 8.73,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "This is in the middle\nof that process.",
        "start": 12.33,
        "duration": 1.755
    },
    {
        "text": "--that kind of moment.\"",
        "start": 16.92,
        "duration": 1.05
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Simply speaking, it's\njust something like",
        "start": 27.39,
        "duration": 3.03
    },
    {
        "text": "'Mission: Impossible,' the TV\nseries when I was a little",
        "start": 30.42,
        "duration": 3.01
    },
    {
        "text": "kid.",
        "start": 33.43,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "I was a huge fan.",
        "start": 33.93,
        "duration": 2.05
    },
    {
        "text": "And this some kind of\nnerdy family version",
        "start": 35.98,
        "duration": 3.83
    },
    {
        "text": "of 'Mission: Impossible.'\"",
        "start": 39.81,
        "duration": 1.71
    },
    {
        "text": "\"In this moment\nfor the young son,",
        "start": 61.83,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "he is kind of manipulator.",
        "start": 64.16,
        "duration": 3.19
    },
    {
        "text": "He controls everything.",
        "start": 67.35,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "And he has a plan.",
        "start": 69.27,
        "duration": 2.18
    },
    {
        "text": "When they rehearse, it looks\nlike a kind of filmmaking.",
        "start": 71.45,
        "duration": 4.84
    },
    {
        "text": "It is like the\nson is director,",
        "start": 76.29,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "the father is the actor.\"",
        "start": 78.69,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I intentionally shoot\nthose shots very quickly",
        "start": 108.66,
        "duration": 5.94
    },
    {
        "text": "and some very spontaneous\nreaction and sudden, small,",
        "start": 114.6,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "improvised.",
        "start": 118.38,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "And something happened\nvery naturally.",
        "start": 119.82,
        "duration": 2.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Rolling the camera, that\nkind of momentary feeling",
        "start": 121.9,
        "duration": 3.59
    },
    {
        "text": "is very important.\"",
        "start": 125.49,
        "duration": 2.44
    }
]